    "entity_type": "person",
    "side": "Bábí",
    "is_new": true,
    "db_statements": [
      "His arrival at his native town, which a certain Karbilá’í Valí-‘Aṭṭár announced to his companions.",
      "ordered, in the fury of his despair, that the tongue of Karbilá’í Valí-‘Aṭṭár be immediately cut out."
